title: Milo Manara: Pandora's Eyes (Humanoids US) (2009 / 2010) (Pudgy)
description:
Contains:   Pandora's Eyes (2009, 2010) (Pudgy)



             " Pandora is a beautiful young woman living with her adoptive parents
               in a major European city. Out of the blue, she learns that her real
               father might be a terrible mob boss wanted by the international
               authorities. When she is kidnapped and taken to Turkey, she is forced
               to confront her dangerous past and investigate the motives of the
               people closest to her. "
